product_name: OllyDog Nightlife II Reflective Dog Collar - Small - 2013 Overstock
long_description: A safety essential for evening dog walks, the small OllyDog Nightlife II Reflective dog collar features bright colors and reflective detailing. Nylon webbing is strong, durable and light. Reflective stripe runs entire length of collar for enhanced visibility in the dark. OllyDog Nightlife II dog collar features an adjustable, quick-release buckle and a metal D-ring for tags and leash attachment. Overstock.
